Package: composr
Title: Create composite variables from survey data
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person("Ethan", "Morrow", , "emorrow3@illinois.edu", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0002-4308-7607"))
Description: This package automates the creation of composite variables from survey data. Using naming conventions of the items, composr detects items that belong to the same scale. It can also calculate basic descriptive statistics, such as the mean, standard deviation, and Cronbach Alpha for composite variables.
